reviewText: Great retro flying squad series albeit a bit unpolished but that's part of the appeal

love me some sweeney! started watching new tricks and that lead me to the sweeney because of dennis waterman. also love john thaw ( memory eternal) so i thought it was a winning proposition-- and so far it is! really enjoying it and since one car looks the same as any other to me, it could be set in any decade.
Best TV detective show ever, classic stuff!
